@startuml seq-21-preferences
' 序列图21：修改用户偏好
title 修改用户偏好序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "settings.js" as Front
participant "UserController" as Ctrl
participant "UserService" as Svc
participant "UserMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 在设置页调整偏好(难度/分类等)
User -> Front: 点击"保存"
Front -> Ctrl: PUT /api/user/preferences/{userId}
Ctrl -> Svc: updatePreferences(userId,preferences)
Svc -> Mapper: update(userId,preferences)
Mapper -> DB: UPDATE user SET preferences=? WHERE user_id=?
DB --> Mapper: 影响行数1
Mapper --> Svc: 成功
Svc --> Ctrl: 成功
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200}
Front -> Front: 更新本地缓存
Front --> User: 提示保存成功

@enduml
